{"tid":2112926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英最高法院院長：國安法下視乎香港法治情況 再決定會否繼續來香港擔任法官","createTime":"2020-07-17T17:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T18:21:09.000Z","uid":7542,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc631860cf8c703e3c4e11a6a6d274c5179753a","tid":2112926,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>明明祖國已經講咗國安法可以維護法治</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身兼英國最高法院院長的香港終審法院非常任法官韋彥德發表聲明，表示「港區國安法」引起關注，影響將視乎法例如何執行，目前有待觀察，英國最高法院將會與英國政府繼續評估香港的情況，英國最高法院法官能否繼續在香港擔任法官，視乎他們的工作是否仍然符合司法獨立及法治。<br />\n<br />\n韋彥德在聲明中強調，英國最高法院支持香港法官維護司法獨立與法治，認為終審法院的法官，毫無疑問會致力維護《基本法》第85條，即是法院獨立行使司法權，不受任何干預，又引述終審法院首席法官馬道立早前說，司法機構的獨立與法治，是香港社會的基石，認為保持及維護司法機構的獨立性與法治，是香港司法機構的使命及憲制責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538465-20200718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538465-20200718.htm&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpZ4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=ff99d346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538465-20200718.htm&h=cff0bb84\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538465-20200718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dccc9899fac17e8992c38708286bcbfabbe286c8","tid":2112926,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">唔知英國最高法院院長係咪擔心呢樣野呢：</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBufF8VPWDZg&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpZ4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=423231b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg</a>"},{"pid":"19b2fe8552a556d5114af28046e785490165755a","tid":2112926,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T